pip install flask-sqlit3 //to install SQL lite3
sudo apt-get install python-virtualenv
pip install flask //flask

Navigate to the folder which contains cms.py(/home/ubuntu/CMS) and run the file

Now open your browser and type http://localhost:5000/create this creates the database

then type http://localhost:5000/addNewMember to add a member to the club
type http://localhost:5000/addNewEvent to add an event in the club and so onnn


rest of the API calls can be found in cms.py beside app.route


In case of any errrs check conn = sqlite3.connect('/home/ubuntu/CMS/database.db')
  place your files appropriately -> /home/ubuntu/CMS/database.db